## JavaScript Clock 

## Overview
This project is a **digital clock** built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**.  
It displays the current time dynamically and updates every second — a great beginner-friendly project to demonstrate your skills in DOM manipulation and time functions.

---

## Features
- Real-time clock display
- Dynamic updating every second
- Clean and responsive UI
- Built with vanilla JavaScript (no frameworks)

---

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6+)

